Mad Slums Direction - Metropolis is a real open world with its own rules and street laws. Feel free to race online with the open world or go through missions among which there are races without rules 2 rivals and you are trying to come first despite the superiority of the wheelbarrows of rivals. Lead your criminal case in the game first-person shooter action constantly leads to unexpected turns of the plot.
Play cool cool games perform exciting missions in the new beautiful metropolis, immerse yourself in the atmosphere into a vibrant and dynamically developing city with a dark side - the criminal inclinations of its inhabitants. Enjoy the games not for money, games without wifi shooting. At a certain stage of becoming a criminal, you can start your auto business in the form of resale gray cars.
The city is full of weapons stores - buy steep cannons and start setting your rules on the streets of the city. Buy, steal, drive cool cars - because all car dealers want to work with you. Increase your driving skill by passing interesting racing assignments.
Be attentive with local law enforcement agencies, because at first glance they seem sluggish and dull, but in fact for the slightest Your virtual game misdemeanor or the slightest shot are ready to tie you and your people in the city, and then believe me, they will have several unsolved cases to hang on you.

Features:
- Deliver trouble to cops and enemies, become a steep gangster;
- Leave your mark on the asphalt to prove that you are the best racer in the game;
- Local mafiosi will turn out on the wrong side to prevent You into the leaders;
- Adjust the graphics to breathtaking performance, enjoy;
- The plot of the missions is reminiscent of a film with a multi-million budget.

Take an active part in the game, go through complex missions, and who knows tomorrow maybe You will become the main mafia in this quiet and cozy at first glance megalopolis, you will live full gangster life to the full!
